Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:37.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:42.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an6\3c&HFFFFFF&\be1\bord0.5\shad2\pos(1151,502)}Anti{\fnNyala}{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Angel Operations Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:40.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me test out my new move on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:42.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I call it the "120{\fnNyala}-{\r}Hour Beating"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, hey, yo, let's dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:47.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey come on, it'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:51.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}New move! New move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:55.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so cute, aren't they Shiina{\fnNyala}-{\r}san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How shallow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:58.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, an elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:06.52,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll go ask Oyama{\fnNyala}-{\r}senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.63,0:02:07.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All we do is take on more brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:11.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking to me, scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:12.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am your God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You still on about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were clinging onto Otonashi and crying like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:23.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The one crying will be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:26.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you will realize the greatness of clothespins,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:30.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and in comparison, your worthlessness, and despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:37.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A clothespin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:38.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You pin it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:39.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You pin it and it doesn't fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The laundry doesn't get dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:42.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:46.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use it instead of a paper clip or just about anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nothing compared to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:53.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no hope for me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:53.36,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't use hypnotism to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:55.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\r}san, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:59.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He came at me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:02.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of that is gentle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:07.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a grown man on his knees crying like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:08.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\r}kun, Naoi{\fnNyala}-{\r}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:19.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an6\3c&HFFFFFF&\be1\bord0.5\shad3\pos(1151,502)}Staff Building 3rd Floor — Empty room
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:16.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you call us all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:22.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoi{\fnNyala}-{\r}kun, I want you to try to recover Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\r}kun's lost memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you giving me orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:26.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:29.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And your superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do what she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:31.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:33.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoi{\fnNyala}-{\r}kun's hypnotism is the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:41.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He can make you regain your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:42.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to give that a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just go ahead and decide that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you don't want them back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I want to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:58.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do I feel so insecure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:05.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I might not be able to live like this if I regain my memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:06.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:07.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:12.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I enjoy living with everyone like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:19.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get my memories back, will I still be able to go on like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:22.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.19,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\r}kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y{\fnNyala}-{\r}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:26.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:30.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of past you had, don't lose sight of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:35.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, I'll be here by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here too, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:42.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's with this difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:47.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:49.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I'll begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii{\fnNyala}-{\r}chan, is school fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:08.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:11.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be fun if you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:14.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if I was smart. {FOTC: The proper conjugation for the subjunctive case is "if I were". But he's not supposed to be.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:15.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:19.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place for kids with bad grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't studying fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:22.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it could be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:23.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is called studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is playing with your friends fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:30.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more fun watching TV or playing games by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:37.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain getting dragged around for other people's hobbies and laughing at jokes that aren't even funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:38.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:41.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to make friends too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:46.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:54.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Onii{\fnNyala}-{\r}chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:03.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'm living for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know my purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:07.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:11.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,because it's easier to live without caring about anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:15.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just working enough to eat and get into a daily routine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was all I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:23.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I kept going to see my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:27.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I would buy her comics with what little money I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:35.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I always got her whatever I picked up first at the bookstore, so I didn't even know if I gave her the same one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:41.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For all I knew, it might have been a different one, and the next part of the story wasn't in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:41.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Onii{\fnNyala}-{\r}chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister would always say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:50.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She would be happy with whatever I got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:53.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was different from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She had hope in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:58.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She could find her purpose in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:03.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But she hadn't been discharged for the last two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could change places with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:11.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I, who didn't have a purpose or meaning in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:16.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That compassion was what kept me visiting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:24.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Working during the summer is hard, but working in the winter is worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:27.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fingers go numb, like they're going to fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept going so I could live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Live?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:40.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I think about it, I might stop working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:43.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:46.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And to buy presents for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:51.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:57.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask the doctor if I can take her outside on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But she can't use a wheelchair if there's snow on the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:03.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:06.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just her, I can carry her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll buy whatever she wants from any store she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:13.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give her a cake from a good store too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case I'll have to save more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:21.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could go outside on Christmas, where would you like to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:23.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The main street!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:24.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be fine with just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:28.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But they put lights on all the trees you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't go there on Christmas anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They started doing it last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor was talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about we go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:45.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask if you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they say no, I'll sneak you out and take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:48.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:49.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Onii{\fnNyala}-{\r}chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:57.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the biggest thank you she gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:01.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:05.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I started working multiple jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:08.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I would come home only to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:11.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was working so hard because I had a goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:18.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My only concern was that her condition was getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't give her permission to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:31.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I snuck in after visiting hours ended and took her into town at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:40.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:42.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:43.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I came to see this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:53.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have even more fun from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:55.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First I'll get you a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:56.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:10:01.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've saved up lots of spending money just for this day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll get you anything, no matter how expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:04.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we start by going to the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We could even go to a jewelers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you'd prefer a normal department store?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:11.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii{\fnNyala}-{\r}chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:21.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's even more after we go shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:22.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do dinner for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:29.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about this stuff, but I got a reservation for a great restaurant I saw in a magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:31.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They make a set meal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A full course dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:41.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I continued to walk and talk by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:44.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:46.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you'll be okay staying by yourself there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:50.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I worry about you though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run into any problems, tell me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can eat here anytime you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:04.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking care of me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:11.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a purpose I'd been living for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:15.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a reason for living close by to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd just never noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:21.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All I wanted to hear was "thank you".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was all it took for me to continue living.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt alive when she expressed her gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:32.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never noticed until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:41.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was such a special person to me, and I did nothing for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:48.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She spent all her time in that hospital, with nothing but the comics I brought her to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:51.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:53.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That meager existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was probably happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:03.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And now that I've lost her, is my life over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:07.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Days full of happiness that I never noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:11.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:15.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and now there's nothing left for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your recovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:25.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:36.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to find another purpose in life.
Comment: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\blur3\t(1200,1500,\blur0)}Book: Medical Encyclopedia
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Book: Medical Encyclopedia
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I might discover a new meaning in living.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:45.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Devoting this life to help someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Card: University Enrollment Selection Form — Otonashi Yuzuru
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have your memories returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:24.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like it was exactly a wonderful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you leave me alone for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:47.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me the meaning to the pointless, worthless life I was living...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:52.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And after I found it, I died trying to reach my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:55.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Without accomplishing a single thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:58.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:01.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I die like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatsune!{miku!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you calmed down a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:16.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:20.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's normal to become unsteady after recovering your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:27.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:30.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've realized again how strong you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So has anything changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can carry on fighting with the Battlefront?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:43.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:44.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't die like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:45.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:48.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've found a purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:49.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, I'll be in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:03.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\pos(640,506)\be1\c&HC1BDC0&}Principal's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:03.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your report?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:06.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're short on meal tickets today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:07.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go with Tornado?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:13.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, today's operation will be Monster Stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're actually going to do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Carnival of despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:24.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are monsters here in this world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the master of the river. {川の主?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:28.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Master of the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a river a short walk from here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to pick up food from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:38.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,D{\fnNyala}-{\r}Don't tell me you just mean river fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:39.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:46.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got tricked into imagining something stupid again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:52.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an6\3c&HFFFFFF&\be1\bord0.5\shad3\pos(1151,502)}Botanical Garden
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who'll win this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:57.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here? {eating butterflies.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:09.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Weeding, among other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:15.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:17.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now we're all going river fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:22.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,River?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:24.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's against regulations to go down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:25.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:30.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the student council president anymore so break a rule for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still a student...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing, bringing her along...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:49.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:50.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The archnemesis of the Battlefront!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:53.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How shallow{\fnNyala}-{\r}minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, she's harmless now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:17:00.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was still originally the student council president!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:03.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, the current acting president is also here with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:04.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:06.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, my position as God comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you're not God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:16.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not the student council president anymore so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:19.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:21.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking on some crazy members...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:25.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just noticed, did no one bring any equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:27.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We already contacted Guild, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:31.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an6\3c&HFFFFFF&\be1\bord0.5\shad3\pos(1151,502)}Below Contact Bridge 2 — Riverbank
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:30.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone crazy about this stuff in Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:38.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:40.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's called Saitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:45.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He also knows about guns, but he's crazy about fishing so we call him Fish Saitou at Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:51.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For this operation, he brings loads of fishing gear up with him on that cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He brings them all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much does he like fishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically he's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:58.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.{is this line あほだな? }
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:21.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'd be your friend in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if there are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are none.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:28.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there were, they'd all disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:32.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:34.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's okay to be friends with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:37.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, join in fishing with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's now how you do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:52.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First you put a lure or bait on the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:57.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not bothered by insects, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:01.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Face the river and swing the rod with all your might!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeyama!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:14.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some monstrous strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:19.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Overdrive works passively.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Passively?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You might just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:25.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You might just be able to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Reel in the master of the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:33.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a monster, like the operation name suggests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's tugging.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:49.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,M{\fnNyala}-{\r}Monster Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:54.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally we take Monster Stream as proof of the master's anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:56.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When this happens we all evacuate.{last word? 離脱？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But with her, just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:03.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're seriously going to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:04.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how big is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:05.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The rod's going to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:08.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate my skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:10.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's made to withstand even the master of the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:13.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it'll be impossible like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:15.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're going to fight with the master?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:17.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita 5th Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:20.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a bowl of meat udon, so help us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:21.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:25.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, Hinata{\fnNyala}-{\r}senpai, you're an open target!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:27.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, how about I kick you with all my might?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:31.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop thinking up stupid things and help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We need more of you in the battle!{もっとだ合戦しろ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:34.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:36.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:42.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on you runts, can't you pull any harder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:50.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:48.39,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:57.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She reeled it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:58.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And pulled us up too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:20:59.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one's the monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:00.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,..a bad situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:04.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fall like this, we'll be eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crazy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,God doesn't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How shallow minded...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna get swallowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:14.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Must save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:29.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, with all this, we won't have to use Tornado for a while, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:30.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to eat this every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:33.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, how are we going to preserve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:36.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be good to waste it either...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:37.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No choice, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:40.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we prepare it all at once and serve it to the ordinary students too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:42.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:51.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is almost like we're doing charity work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:54.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gone from being a battlefront to some kind of volunteer group.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:59.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have an opponent to fight against anymore, so won't we stop being a battlefront?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:02.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what will we be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:06.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Slack so we don't vanish team"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop chop chop chop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:14.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought we'd end up doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:20.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Tachibana, mind if I call you by your first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:23.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've become friends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:24.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:26.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.30,0:22:29.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We fished together, cooked together,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:31.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I've always thought from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.57,0:22:34.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such a pretty name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:37.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:40.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade means "to play a tune" right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.64,0:22:43.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to take it like that, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.45,0:22:49.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Yuzuru, written like "tie a bow". {弦を結ぶ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:50.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:55.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kanade, I want you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:56.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.78,0:23:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay with us from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:01.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:04.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want you to fight with anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:06.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to enjoy your time with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.73,0:23:11.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:14.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want to be with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:15.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:18.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so, I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.67,0:23:22.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:23.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:30.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:32.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, she hasn't been around...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:35.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably just watching over us from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:39.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like she's the type to participate in this kind of volunteer work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.69,0:23:41.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, help us out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:45.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:49.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe, who got you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:51.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.82,0:23:52.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:58.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kanade's been with me the entire time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.45,0:24:10.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel?
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< preview >
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:18.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita 5th Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:19.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we're closed in...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.42,0:24:19.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray we can meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.24,0:24:20.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.22,0:24:22.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take on something that scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.14,0:24:20.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.99,0:24:22.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.24,0:24:23.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you one possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.68,0:24:22.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is Kanade okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.68,0:24:22.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ANGEL PLAYER...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.85,0:24:24.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll persuade them by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.25,0:24:23.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So shallow minded...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.54,0:24:25.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the time has come to show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.10,0:24:25.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Leave the one's we don't make it in time for!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.11,0:24:25.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:27.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be okay, Kanade!
